esar-6-scaled.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eBut, alas, I figured it out for you so we can have the best crab cake caesar at home.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eIt’s a texture lovers’ dream!\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/crab-cake-caesar-8-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"crab cake caesar with old bay croutons\" width=\"1651\" height=\"2200\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2025/03/crab-cake-caesar/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"Crab Cake Caesar with Old Bay Croutons.\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/crab-cake-caesar-8-scaled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/crab-cake-caesar-8-scaled.jpg 1651w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/crab-cake-caesar-8-728x970.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/crab-cake-caesar-8-768x1024.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/crab-cake-caesar-8-1152x1536.jpg 1152w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/crab-cake-caesar-8-1537x2048.jpg 1537w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/crab-cake-caesar-8-640x853.jpg 640w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/crab-cake-caesar-8-150x200.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1651px) 100vw, 1651px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201651%202200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/crab-cake-caesar-8-scaled.jpg 1651w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/crab-cake-caesar-8-728x970.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/crab-cake-caesar-8-768x1024.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/crab-cake-caesar-8-1152x1536.jpg 1152w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/crab-cake-caesar-8-1537x2048.jpg 1537w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/crab-cake-caesar-8-640x853.jpg 640w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/crab-cake-caesar-8-150x200.jpg 150w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/crab-cake-caesar-8-scaled.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eFirst up, I put ritz crackers instead of saltines in my crab cakes. Hello, huge win! So buttery and perfect. \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eNext, I made super seasoned old bay croutons. I used a multigrain sourdough bread, olive oil and old bay then toasted those babies until golden brown. Delish. \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/crab-cake-caesar-4-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"crab cake caesar with old bay croutons\" width=\"1658\" height=\"2200\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2025/03/crab-cake-caesar/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"Crab Cake Caesar with Old Bay Croutons.\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/crab-cake-caesar-4-scaled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/crab-cake-caesar-4-scaled.jpg 1658w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/crab-cake-caesar-4-728x966.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/crab-cake-caesar-4-768x1019.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/crab-cake-caesar-4-1158x1536.jpg 1158w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/crab-cake-caesar-4-1544x2048.jpg 1544w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/crab-cake-caesar-4-150x199.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1658px) 100vw, 1658px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201658%202200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/crab-cake-caesar-4-scaled.jpg 1658w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/crab-cake-caesar-4-728x966.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/crab-cake-caesar-4-768x1019.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/crab-cake-caesar-4-1158x1536.jpg 1158w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/crab-cake-caesar-4-1544x2048.jpg 1544w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/crab-cake-caesar-4-150x199.jpg 150w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/crab-cake-caesar-4-scaled.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAdd in my caesar dressing, crisp romaine and some shaved parmesan and this is IT.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eIt’s just it.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch3\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe crab cake caesar we all need to make this season! \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eDelicious, feels a little fancy, tastes amazing, is super satisfying and crunchy.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThis checks all the boxes for me and I LOVE IT. \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/crab-cake-caesar-5-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"crab cake caesar with old bay croutons\" width=\"1637\" height=\"2200\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2025/03/crab-cake-caesar/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"Crab Cake Caesar with Old Bay Croutons.\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/crab-cake-caesar-5-scaled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/crab-cake-caesar-5-scaled.jpg 1637w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/crab-cake-caesar-5-728x978.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/crab-cake-caesar-5-768x1032.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/crab-cake-caesar-5-1143x1536.jpg 1143w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/crab-cake-caesar-5-1524x2048.jpg 1524w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/crab-cake-caesar-5-150x202.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1637px) 100vw, 1637px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201637%202200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/crab-cake-caesar-5-scaled.jpg 1637w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/crab-cake-caesar-5-728x978.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/crab-cake-caesar-5-768x1032.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/crab-cake-caesar-5-1143x1536.jpg 1143w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/crab-cake-caesar-5-1524x2048.jpg 1524w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/crab-cake-caesar-5-150x202.jpg 150w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/crab-cake-caesar-5-scaled.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThese crab cakes were my grandma’s recipe with just a few tweaks. They have very little filler. It’s important to get GOOD jumbo lump crab meat. That will make sure these taste like restaurant quality crab cakes. \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan id=\"more-98286\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/crab-cake-caesar-7-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"crab cake caesar with old bay croutons\" width=\"1715\" height=\"2200\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2025/03/crab-cake-caesar/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"Crab Cake Caesar with Old Bay Croutons.\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/crab-cake-caesar-7-scaled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/crab-cake-caesar-7-scaled.jpg 1715w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/crab-cake-caesar-7-728x934.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/crab-cake-caesar-7-768x985.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/crab-cake-caesar-7-1197x1536.jpg 1197w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/crab-cake-caesar-7-1596x2048.jpg 1596w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/crab-cake-caesar-7-150x192.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1715px) 100vw, 1715px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201715%202200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/crab-cake-caesar-7-scaled.jpg 1715w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/crab-cake-caesar-7-728x934.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/crab-cake-caesar-7-768x985.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/crab-cake-caesar-7-1197x1536.jpg 1197w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/crab-cake-caesar-7-1596x2048.jpg 1596w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/crab-cake-caesar-7-150x192.jpg 150w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/crab-cake-caesar-7-scaled.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eMy greek yogurt caesar is SO easy and can be made ahead of time. Keep it in the fridge for a few days. It calls for anchovy paste and I can’t express how important this is! It really adds the classic caesar flavor. It’s a paste, so it’s super easy to work with too.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/crab-cake-caesar-9-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"crab cake caesar with old bay croutons\" width=\"1817\" height=\"2200\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2025/03/crab-cake-caesar/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"Crab Cake Caesar with Old Bay Croutons.\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/crab-cake-caesar-9-scaled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/crab-cake-caesar-9-scaled.jpg 1817w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/crab-cake-caesar-9-728x882.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/crab-cake-caesar-9-768x930.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/crab-cake-caesar-9-1268x1536.jpg 1268w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/crab-cake-caesar-9-1691x2048.jpg 1691w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/crab-cake-caesar-9-150x182.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1817px) 100vw, 1817px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201817%202200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/crab-cake-caesar-9-scaled.jpg 1817w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/crab-cake-caesar-9-728x882.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/crab-cake-caesar-9-768x930.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/crab-cake-caesar-9-1268x1536.jpg 1268w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/crab-cake-caesar-9-1691x2048.jpg 1691w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/crab-cake-caesar-9-150x182.jpg 150w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/crab-cake-caesar-9-scaled.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe croutons are self explanatory. And incredible. Make extra, because if you’re anything like me, you won’t be able to stop eating them off the pan! \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/crab-cake-caesar-12-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"crab cake caesar with old bay croutons\" width=\"1747\" height=\"2200\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2025/03/crab-cake-caesar/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"Crab Cake Caesar with Old Bay Croutons.\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/crab-cake-caesar-12-scaled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/crab-cake-caesar-12-scaled.jpg 1747w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/crab-cake-caesar-12-728x917.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/crab-cake-caesar-12-768x967.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/crab-cake-caesar-12-1220x1536.jpg 1220w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/crab-cake-caesar-12-1626x2048.jpg 1626w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/crab-cake-caesar-12-150x189.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1747px) 100vw, 1747px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201747%202200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/crab-cake-caesar-12-scaled.jpg 1747w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/crab-cake-caesar-12-728x917.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/crab-cake-caesar-12-768x967.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/crab-cake-caesar-12-1220x1536.jpg 1220w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/crab-cake-caes